  <h3>How to Earn Points?</h3>
  <p>
    For every IDR 1,000 spent on your purchase, you will earn 1 point. This means that every time you make a purchase, the amount you spend directly translates into points that accumulate in your account.
  </p>

  <h4>Example:</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>If you spend IDR 10,000 on a purchase, you will earn 10 points.</li>
    <li>If you spend IDR 50,000, you will earn 50 points.</li>
    <li>If you spend IDR 100,000, you will earn 100 points.</li>
  </ul>

  <ol>
    <li>
      <h3>Earning Points from Purchases</h3>
      <p>
