  <h3>How to Redeem Points?</h3>
  <p>
    Now that you have accumulated points, the next step is to redeem them for discounts on future purchases. Here’s how it works:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>For every 100 points, you can redeem a discount of IDR 2,000 on your next purchase.</li>
    <li>You can redeem points in multiples. This means that if you accumulate more than 100 points, you can redeem them for a larger discount.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Example of Redeeming Points:</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>100 points = IDR 2,000 discount</li>
    <li>200 points = IDR 4,000 discount</li>
    <li>500 points = IDR 10,000 discount</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    So, if you have 500 points, you can redeem those points for a discount of IDR 10,000 on your next purchase. The more points you collect, the higher the discount you can get!
  </p>

